column5: Heading up Wed. Does anyone have an update on walleyes and crappies?ThanksBill K

I've heard the crappies are starting to stack up near Thompson Creek, and walleyes can be found in 20-23' on the flats. I'm going up Oct. 4 for a nine day trip. Let us know how you did. Where are you staying? Weather should be nice and cool for you.
RockptGo to www.livejournal.com/users/buenavista to get a report on fishing in Morson. Buena Vista Resort puts it out.
